\fs28 \cf0 DNSUpdate 2
\f1\b0  is a client for dynamic DNS services like DynDNS.org and ZoneEdit.com, specific to MacOS X. It uses the Cocoa framework and is launched at boot time. It comes with a graphic application to configure and monitor the client.\
